data.description: Jefferson City Schools! 1+ acre lot NO HOA! Charming home located minutes from downtown Jefferson. 3 bed/2 bath features an oversized master on main, HUGE custom walk in shower with bench. Oversized secondary bedrooms located on second floor featuring a separate full bathroom. Kitchen features beautiful white cabinetry, stainless steel appliances, and granite countertops, and tile backsplash. LVP throughout the entire house! . Walk out the back door to relax on the screened in covered porch that overlooks a large fenced in backyard. Newer roof, HVAC, etc. Great location close to schools, shopping, and minutes from I-85!
